'''天主教萨莱诺总教区'''是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[意大利|意大利]]南部[[坎帕尼亚|坎帕尼亚]]大区设立的一个教区，成立于10世纪，1818年合并Acerno教区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dscai.html |title=''Catholic Hierarchy'' page |access-date=2008-10-27 |archive-date=2022-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220108171741/https://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dscai.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

現任總主教為{{link-it|安德肋·貝蘭迪|Andrea Bellandi}}<ref name="Vatican20190504">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/04/190504b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810161045/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/04/190504b.html |archivedate=2019-08-10 |language=en |date=2019-05-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|吉拉·皮耶羅|Gerardo Pierro}}和{{link-en|類斯·莫雷蒂 (總主教)|Luigi Moretti (archbishop)|類斯·莫雷蒂}}<ref name="Vatican20190504" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 10.06.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/06/10/0382/00869.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810171546/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/06/10/0382/00869.html |archivedate=2019-08-10 |language=it |date=2010-06-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

